<Layout title="Blog - Rajesh D'Souza">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Blog</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-400 text-xl mb-12 max-w-3xl">
      Welcome to my blog where I share my thoughts and experiences on technology, business operations, and personal growth. 
      Here you'll find articles about improving operational efficiency, implementing automation, and lessons learned from 
      working with various startups.
    </p>

    <div class="grid gap-6">
      <a href="/blog/post-1" class="block bg-[#1A1D24] p-8 rounded-lg hover:bg-[#1A1D24]/80 transition-colors">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Card Title 1</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">Brief description of the content goes here...</p>
        <span class="text-[#00DC82] flex items-center gap-2">
          Read More 
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12.293 5.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
